originalText.text: I mostly worked with Anisa Gjoni but also with Mikkle Morales (Mike). Anisa and Mike were both very responsive and easy to contact as well as forthcoming with answers to my questions and transparent about what to expect next at each step of the process. I found them via a Facebook marketplace listing for an apartment in NYC and was able to do a virtual tour, meet my roommate, and sign the least all within one week of establishing contact. Definitely recommend working with them!

originalText.text: Anisa Gjoni helped my roommate and I find the perfect apartment. She was very communicative, responsive, patient, and answered any questions we had. Would definitely recommend her.

originalText.text: Mike Morales was excellent to work with in finding our new apartment! Very quick communication and listened to our ideal needs. Only showed us spaces that fit our descriptions!! Plus, had very great videos of the spaces so you knew exactly what the layout was before viewing.

originalText.text: The Universal Realty team, with specific mention of Mikkle Morales, have been such a help in locking into a new home! Mikkle was transparent and down to earth, providing realistic answers to all of my questions. He, and Jason Pilku, were quite responsive, and lowered my anxiety about the whole process by giving my situation personal attention, working to make it a smooth, streamlined process. Thanks kindly, ya'll! Best, Isa
